description: "A detailed late 17th century map of Asia, showing ancient kingdoms and the place names of important settlements. The cartouche features a drawing of Asian traders selling their goods, while a camel, monkey and two birds look on."
label: "India orientalis, cum adjacentibus insulis nova delineatione ob oculos polita / per Matthaeum Seutter, S.C.M. Geogr. August."
